===Etymology 2===
From {{inh|en|enm|ȝeld}}, from {{inh|en|ang|ġield}}, from {{inh|en|gmw-pro|*geld}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*geldą||reward, gift, money}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*gʰeldʰ-||to pay}}.
{{rel-top|Cognates}}
Compare {{cog|fy|jild}}, {{cog|nl|geld}}, Low German and {{cog|de|Geld}}, {{cog|da|gæld}}, {{cog|sv|gäld}}, {{cog|is|gjald}}. See also {{m|en|geld}}.
